RawLine: TNPC_60076752,大福叔你是在{color=#FF0000}未時{/color}鑄劍，而劍鋒派與飛白派弟子，委託鑄劍時辰都是{color=#FF0000}午時{/color}。從飛白派的語氣聽來如此肯定，我想一定是他先的了。,大福叔你是在{color=#FF0000}未时{/color}铸剑，而剑锋派与飞白派弟子，委托铸剑时辰都是{color=#FF0000}午时{/color}。从飞白派的语气听来如此肯定，我想一定是他先的了。

Items.mt: Uncle Dafu, you cast the sword at the hour of midnight, and the disciples of the Jianfeng and the Fei Bai Sects, both commissioned to cast the sword at midday. From the tone of the Fei Bai faction sounds so sure, I think it must be his first.
